# URL Shortener Backend


A robust URL shortener service built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB that allows users to create short URLs and track click analytics.

## Features

- âœ¨ Shorten long URLs to compact, shareable links
- ğŸ“Š Click tracking and analytics
- ğŸ—ï¸ Clean MVC architecture with separate layers (Controllers, Services, DAO)
- ğŸ”— Automatic URL redirection
- ğŸš€ Fast and lightweight using nanoid for URL generation
- ğŸ“± RESTful API design
- âš ï¸ Comprehensive error handling with custom error classes
- ğŸ”„ Try-catch wrapper for async operations

## Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM
- **URL Generation**: nanoid library
- **Environment Management**: dotenv

