- `dotenv` - Environment variable management
- `nanoid` - Unique ID generation

## Known Issues

âš ï¸ **Bug in Service Layer**: The [`createShortUrlWithoutUser`](Backend/src/services/shortUrl.service.js) function currently saves a hardcoded short URL ("2IKaH3") instead of the generated one. This needs to be fixed:

```javascript
// Current (incorrect):
await saveShortUrl("2IKaH3", url);

// Should be:
await saveShortUrl(shortUrl, url);
```

